title: Trend Asunder 4/22: Earth Day, Honey Boo Boo, Las Vegas, Kim Jong Un

description:
On this edition of Trend Asunder Jack and Miles discuss Earth Day and how others are celebrating indoors, Honey Boo Boo may have been pregnant at 14 but it was fake, Las Vegas is potentially opening prematurely - offered up by the Mayor as a control group for spread, Kim Jong Un has gone into surgery and potentially succeeded by his sister, Kim Yo Jong.
